sources.title: Battle B-Boy | Full Movie | Action Drama | Matt Kohler
sources.description:
Battle B-Boy - A group of talented but financially struggling B-Boys join an underground fighting ring in Downtown Los Angeles that uses Hip-Hop music and Break dancing to battle for money. To save the life of one of their friend's father, the B-Boys form a strong bond. They fight for each other, for their families and for a better future.
2016.  Stars: Matt Kohler, Megan Le, Shauna Baker, Jae Phan, Alison Dahlstrom, Ricky Cole
